data.text:
Martin Eichelberger and Alyce Faye Eichelberger were married for 8 years. They dated for 2 years after getting together in 1964 and married on 22nd Jan 1966. 8 years later they divorced in 1975.

They had 2 children, Martin Davis (54) and Clinton Charles (51).

About

Alyce Faye Eichelberger is a 79 year old American Radio Personality. Born Alyce Faye McBride on 28th October, 1944 in Frederick, Oklahoma, USA, she is famous for Wine for the Confused. Her zodiac sign is Scorpio.
